Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.10,0:01:49.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The moon is about to disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.13,0:01:52.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!\NA shooting star!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.77,0:01:57.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wish that I can stay by\NMaster Sesshomaru forever and ever.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.67,0:01:59.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Rin...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.31,0:02:01.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't fall behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.58,0:02:02.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.45,0:02:06.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}This strange feeling...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.35,0:02:10.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Evil spirit... Why are you so restless?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.03,0:02:19.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tomorrow is a new moon.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.76,0:02:24.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even the moon has days when\nit can hide in darkness.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.33,0:02:27.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}But with Naraku holding on\nto my heart,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.14,0:02:29.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}there's nowhere for me to run.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.47,0:02:32.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.17,0:02:35.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The demon spirits that Naraku\nkept around him...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.81,0:02:40.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,They've gone through the barrier!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.07,0:02:59.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey! Koga!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.87,0:03:00.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Koga!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.57,0:03:06.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's rest a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.31,0:03:09.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My body won't hold up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.78,0:03:13.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Even the wolves are out\nof breath. Koga!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.02,0:03:15.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.72,0:03:17.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If I had to wait for you,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.65,0:03:20.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,we wouldn't reach Naraku's castle\neven in a hundred years!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.76,0:03:21.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Then Koga...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.86,0:03:25.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You weren't just running around\nhere and there?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.09,0:03:29.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I can smell it.\NThis foul odor.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.30,0:03:32.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's close... Naraku's castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.57,0:03:37.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}This time... I'll attack his castle\nand kill him!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.79,0:04:01.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll avenge my comrades who\nwere tricked and slaughtered.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.10,0:04:03.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Without fail!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.07,0:04:10.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Inuyasha?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.74,0:04:13.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Isn't it in this direction?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.94,0:04:16.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shaddup! Don't talk to me!\NI can't concentrate!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.94,0:04:20.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Isn't it useless to sniff the ground\nto find Naraku's castle?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.92,0:04:24.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.62,0:04:27.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha's nose isn't\nworking now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.26,0:04:29.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Tonight is the first night.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.02,0:04:32.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh! The night of the new moon!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.99,0:04:34.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Night of the new moon?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.53,0:04:35.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.73,0:04:39.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Tonight, Inuyasha loses his powers\nand becomes a mortal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.20,0:04:42.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha, let's not do anything\nrash tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.30,0:04:44.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Even if we find Naraku's castle,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.71,0:04:46.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,without your powers,\nyou can't fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.54,0:04:50.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't be ridiculous!\NWe've come this far!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.68,0:04:53.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But! We can't act hastily.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.68,0:04:54.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.72,0:04:57.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's!\NA cyclone?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.35,0:05:00.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's approaching!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.93,0:05:07.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey! Kagome!\NYou're here, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.73,0:05:09.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,K-Koga!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.90,0:05:11.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's what you get for\nsniffing the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.00,0:05:16.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey, mutt! So you followed\nthe smell, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.11,0:05:20.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why you wild wolf!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.08,0:05:23.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.64,0:05:24.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sit!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.25,0:05:29.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Koga, did you come to find\NNaraku's castle?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.35,0:05:32.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah... I don't know what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.69,0:05:35.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,but I'm getting strong whiffs\nof Naraku's foul smell.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.82,0:05:37.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's never happened before.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.93,0:05:38.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That means!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.23,0:05:41.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The barrier around Naraku's castle\nis weakened.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.70,0:05:44.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,In any case, if I follow this smell,\NI'll find his castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.77,0:05:49.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Kagome.\NI'll kill that Naraku...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.21,0:05:52.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm not the one\nyou want...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.97,0:05:54.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No, Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.38,0:05:56.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't stop me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.61,0:05:58.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm gonna settle it\ntoday, once and for all!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.78,0:06:00.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.35,0:06:02.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? What's up, mutt?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.08,0:06:08.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's this? Somehow, you don't\nstink like you usually do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.99,0:06:10.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Didja take a soak in the river?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.43,0:06:10.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,W-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.29,0:06:13.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey! Don't get close to my Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.06,0:06:15.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.03,0:06:17.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If you're jealous,\ntry separating us!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.53,0:06:19.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.17,0:06:21.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey! Koga!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.57,0:06:24.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Caught up with you at last!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.87,0:06:26.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, I have no time for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.21,0:06:28.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,See ya, Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.64,0:06:31.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey! Running away?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.95,0:06:33.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Naraku's head is mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.68,0:06:37.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?! Hey, wait up, Koga!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.39,0:06:39.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, hello, Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.99,0:06:40.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.86,0:06:42.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We're in a rush, so good-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.19,0:06:45.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn him!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.53,0:06:47.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shall we go after him?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.06,0:06:50.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No, better not to do\nanything tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.90,0:06:53.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?! Are you crazy?\NHe's gonna beat us to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.37,0:06:55.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Calm down, Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.24,0:06:57.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Besides Koga,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.44,0:06:59.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,do you want Naraku to see\nyou in your human form?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.14,0:07:02.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If he learns about the day that\na half-demon loses his powers,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.34,0:07:03.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,your life will be in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.38,0:07:06.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And if Naraku is the enemy,\nyou have to be even more careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.08,0:07:13.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Damn! What a time... when Naraku's\nsmell is all over the place!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.03,0:07:27.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn, this castle is stifling!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.27,0:07:31.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,All the vassals who were brought\nhere to this castle...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.41,0:07:35.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,have been exposed to Naraku's\ntoxic barrier and died.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.21,0:07:42.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What is it, Kanna?\NSneaking up from behind like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.35,0:07:47.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}This fellow... He's Koga, the leader\nof the Wolf-Demon Tribe.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.66,0:07:50.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is he near this castle?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.89,0:07:53.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is it a coincidence or...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.30,0:07:58.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kanna, does Naraku know\nabout this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.97,0:08:01.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No... He's not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.97,0:08:07.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's right. Naraku disappears\nonce in a while.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.04,0:08:08.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagura...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.08,0:08:12.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll go and kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.21,0:08:15.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No need to wait for\NNaraku's orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.25,0:08:17.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You'd better stop, Kagura.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.42,0:08:22.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I hate Naraku's way\nof stooping to trickery.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.52,0:08:25.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll kill anyone who has\NSacred Jewel shards.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.49,0:08:27.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Who needs a plan of action?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.30,0:08:31.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's all in Naraku's hand...\nlife and death.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.60,0:08:36.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We are all Naraku's tools.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.64,0:08:39.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Who cares?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.71,0:08:42.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He's not here now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.18,0:08:49.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is a weird fog.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.48,0:08:51.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I can't see a thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.82,0:08:53.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.62,0:08:56.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The smell is strongest right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.16,0:08:59.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It has to be around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.93,0:09:01.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Koga! Up above!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.07,0:09:09.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Skeletons with swords?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.31,0:09:18.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yo! Been awhile, Koga.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.95,0:09:19.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.75,0:09:25.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,W-What's that?!\NThose skeletons!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.29,0:09:28.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,They're the guards of the castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.49,0:09:30.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There're countless numbers\nof them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.96,0:09:32.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wind Sorceress Kagura!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.76,0:09:36.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I haven't forgotten your despicable face,\nnot for one day!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.47,0:09:40.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,After all, you're the one who\nkilled my comrades!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.00,0:09:42.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Prepare to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.84,0:09:45.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's payback time\nfor all you did!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.81,0:09:47.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You should talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.44,0:09:50.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I barely missed taking\nyour Sacred Jewel shards.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.24,0:09:51.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll get them this time, for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.01,0:09:55.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}It'll be easy shutting\ndown Koga's speed.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.52,0:09:56.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll let him dance for me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.65,0:09:58.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Dance of Corpses!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.52,0:10:05.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?! Still resorting to tricks!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.30,0:10:11.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Dance of Blades!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.30,0:10:13.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.21,0:10:19.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.98,0:10:22.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.05,0:10:26.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Fool! I'll cripple you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.12,0:10:30.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Dance of the Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.29,0:10:41.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- W-What?!\N- A whirlpool of bones!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.94,0:10:52.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.94,0:10:55.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now choose your fate, Koga.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.04,0:10:59.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let the skeletons in the whirlpool\ncut you into bits...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.55,0:11:01.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Or jump out\nand be slain by me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.72,0:11:04.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.99,0:11:08.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey! Even Koga doesn't have\na chance in that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.29,0:11:12.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- W-What'll we do?\N- But we're not strong enough...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.10,0:11:22.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why, that bitch!\NShe's enjoying it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.27,0:11:25.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If we can take away that\npowerful fan of hers...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.34,0:11:26.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,maybe we can win.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.01,0:11:28.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah, you're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.91,0:11:30.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So get up close and\nsteal it away!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.91,0:11:32.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- Who?\N- You!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.58,0:11:35.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stupid! She'll notice me before\NI get close
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.08,0:11:37.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and I'll be cut into bits!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.59,0:11:40.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But to fight Kagura and that wind...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.62,0:11:42.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.09,0:11:44.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wind! There IS a way!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.56,0:11:49.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey, Ginta!\NDon't be hasty!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.90,0:11:53.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Koga's actions are proof that
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.00,0:11:56.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Naraku's barrier\nhas become weaker.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.87,0:12:01.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I think we should at least verify\nthe castle's whereabouts.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.14,0:12:04.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But we can't take Inuyasha\nin his state.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.28,0:12:08.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So Miroku and I can go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.42,0:12:10.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And if Inuyasha won't listen,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.79,0:12:13.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,we'll have Kagome\nmake him "sit,"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.42,0:12:15.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,then we can knock him out\nto keep him quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.69,0:12:17.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Not that again?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.63,0:12:20.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Like I said...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.60,0:12:24.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Koga likes to be complimented.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.30,0:12:25.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So l just thought\nif I flattered him,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.07,0:12:28.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,he wouldn't become curious about\nyour sense of smell.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.34,0:12:31.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Still, your eyes were all sparkly!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.24,0:12:35.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You tend to get too chummy\nwith that wild animal.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.21,0:12:37.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I do not!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.58,0:12:38.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You do!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.78,0:12:39.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.38,0:12:41.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.35,0:12:42.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.95,0:12:44.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.09,0:12:46.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.66,0:12:49.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,They're Koga's men.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.46,0:12:50.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha, hide!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.16,0:12:54.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.83,0:12:57.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The Wolf Demon Tribe are here again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.13,0:13:00.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is a bad time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.97,0:13:02.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.57,0:13:03.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Something terrible's happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.11,0:13:06.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.14,0:13:09.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Koga and Kagura are fighting?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.54,0:13:12.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A-And... it doesn't look too good.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.88,0:13:15.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha, you must not show yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.72,0:13:20.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn! Don't worry!\NI don't intend to go help Koga.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.22,0:13:24.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Still... if Kagura's appeared,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.36,0:13:26.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}that means Naraku's castle\nis nearby.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.80,0:13:31.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}But Naraku had put up a barrier\nto prevent us from getting close.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.27,0:13:34.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}This bothers me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.90,0:13:36.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I guess we have to go\nand check.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.07,0:13:37.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sango!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.27,0:13:41.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha, you stay with Kagome.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.71,0:13:43.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You want to keep your mortal\nstate a secret, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.84,0:13:45.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn! No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.65,0:13:52.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What're you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.39,0:13:53.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.65,0:13:56.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now listen here. If you reveal what\nyou see, I'll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.29,0:13:58.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,O-Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.46,0:14:00.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A-All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.66,0:14:01.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.33,0:14:05.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, he shut them up.\NSo shall we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.04,0:14:14.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I can smell blood in the air.\NGo... twist and turn harder!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.65,0:14:21.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Koga?\NToo scared to come out?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.58,0:14:23.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Or...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.65,0:14:25.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you already dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.45,0:14:28.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn! That bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.16,0:14:33.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's useless... No matter how many\nbones I destroy, there're countless more.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.93,0:14:38.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}And my strength won't hold up\nagainst these blades.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.33,0:14:39.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What'll I do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.14,0:14:43.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hmm... Maybe I'll let him out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.17,0:14:48.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If he's in too many pieces,\NI'll have a hard time finding the shards.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.68,0:14:50.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No need to worry about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.91,0:14:54.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? Above?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.32,0:14:55.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.25,0:15:00.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Pretty persistent.\NIs what I'd like to say...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.42,0:15:01.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Prepare to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.43,0:15:10.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn! I can't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.00,0:15:15.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Fool! You can jump or run...\nbut you can't escape my wind!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.20,0:15:16.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Fujin!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.41,0:15:25.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}My Sacred Jewel shards!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.22,0:15:38.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}My Sacred Jewel shards!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.30,0:15:48.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now then...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.57,0:15:51.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm taking the two shards\nfrom your legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.24,0:15:54.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now you're just an ordinary demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.44,0:15:58.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So... it's time for the finishing blow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.91,0:16:00.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.92,0:16:05.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagura!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.86,0:16:14.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Your life's been spared, Koga.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.63,0:16:21.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,She got away!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.24,0:16:23.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku... Koga is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.04,0:16:26.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Koga!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.78,0:16:28.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Your!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.54,0:16:32.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The Sacred Jewel shards were\nremoved from your legs!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.41,0:16:35.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Koga! You're badly wounded.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.22,0:16:37.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll tend to you right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.22,0:16:41.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Leave him alone, Kagome!\NHe's gonna die anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.29,0:16:42.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.89,0:16:46.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.59,0:16:51.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're hopeless, Koga! Getting cut up\nby the likes of Kagura!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.77,0:16:54.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.27,0:16:55.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Looking so weak!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.27,0:17:00.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I suspected Inuyasha was\njust a half-demon...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.28,0:17:02.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He was one, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.75,0:17:08.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I heard that half-demons fear\nfor their lives...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.42,0:17:12.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And when they're in the mortal state,\nthey never appear before an enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.49,0:17:18.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're pretty gutsy... coming around\nme looking like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.13,0:17:23.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now that you know my secret...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.40,0:17:25.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wanna fight?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.13,0:17:29.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shaddup! I'll finish you off right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.61,0:17:32.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Koga!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.81,0:17:35.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is an ointment I brought\nfrom my country.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.34,0:17:38.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It works well on sword cuts.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.18,0:17:40.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Thanks, Kagome.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.98,0:17:44.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why, that... Kagome!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.89,0:17:50.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Serves him right!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.02,0:17:55.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Still... Not only Koga, but even Inuyasha\napproached the castle.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.37,0:18:01.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}That means Naraku's barrier\nis weakened.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.57,0:18:03.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's right!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.54,0:18:06.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Naraku is... not here!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.02,0:18:22.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What a relief.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.36,0:18:28.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah... why should I hand them\nover to Naraku?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.40,0:18:30.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now is the time to escape...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.86,0:18:33.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now when Naraku's barrier\nis weak.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.97,0:18:35.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}But... Naraku has...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.01,0:18:39.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.08,0:18:48.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't ever forget, Kagura.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.05,0:18:52.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Your heart is in my hands!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.05,0:18:55.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Damn!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.72,0:18:59.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can easily turn you back\ninto mere flesh.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.86,0:19:03.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kagura... Do not forget.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.90,0:19:08.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}You are merely a part of my flesh.\NI created you out of me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.37,0:19:11.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Do not forget that.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.14,0:19:15.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn! No! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.25,0:19:22.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I cannot escape from his grasp.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.92,0:19:28.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? A shooting star!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.66,0:19:34.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There is someone!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.57,0:19:39.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.71,0:19:45.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That one!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.38,0:19:53.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}He has the power to sever the bond\nbetween me and Naraku!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.96,0:20:15.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kagura... So you escaped.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.44,0:20:23.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It sparkled! A star just sparkled!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.21,0:20:25.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Did you see, Lord Sesshomaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.82,0:20:37.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Lately, Lord Sesshomaru does things\nthat even I, his vassal, cannot fathom.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.56,0:20:39.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm so lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.03,0:20:43.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This child... She is ignorant of\nmy concerns...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.30,0:20:44.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And sleeps away.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.04,0:20:49.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Lord Sesshomaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.54,0:20:52.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's his scent.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.44,0:20:54.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.08,0:20:58.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.18,0:21:02.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The smell of that fellow who\nwas so rude to you... That Naraku!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.32,0:21:06.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is he nearby?\NW-What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.12,0:21:07.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ohhh!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.83,0:21:17.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.53,0:21:18.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,"Yo"?! Why, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.53,0:21:20.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sesshomaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.13,0:21:23.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Did you follow Naraku's scent, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.14,0:21:25.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Lord Sesshomaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.94,0:21:28.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This woman is the one\NNaraku created from his body...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.94,0:21:32.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wind Sorceress Kagura, I recall?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.75,0:21:36.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm glad you remembered me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.79,0:21:42.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Take your hand off your sword.\NI didn't come here to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.36,0:21:46.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sesshomaru, I want to make\na deal with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.93,0:21:47.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.13,0:21:51.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You know what these are.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.03,0:21:55.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll give these Sacred Jewel\nshards to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.27,0:21:59.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,In return, kill Naraku.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.74,0:22:00.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.68,0:22:04.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Free me from his grip.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.25,0:23:50.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My name is Kagura.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.98,0:23:53.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I am the wind.\NI live freely.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.29,0:23:54.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So you'll betray me, Kagura?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.65,0:23:55.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Silence, Naraku!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.32,0:23:59.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So you're also a half-demon\nwho loses his powers at times.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.86,0:24:00.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Foolish woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.16,0:24:03.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Did you think you could\nescape my clutches?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.03,0:24:07.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I am Kagura. I will live freely\nlike the wind.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.07,0:24:12.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Next on Inuyasha:\N"The Howling Wind of Betrayal"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.27,0:24:15.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I saw you, Inuyasha...\nas a mortal!
